---
title: Primo Prosciutto Sandwiches with Ricotta, Tomato & Balsamic Arugula Salad
description: The only thing better than a really great sandwich is one that takes just minutes to prepare! This Really Great Sandwich starts with toasted flatbreads that have a crunchy pizza crust vibe. Add juicy tomato, salty prosciutto, creamy fresh ricotta, and a tangle of sweet balsamic-dressed arugula. For extra points, there’s a fresh arugula salad on the side. Lunch in 10 minutes doesn’t get better than this!
